s. korean februari current account surplu narrow south korea 's current account surplu narrow to 419 mln dlr in februari from 679 mln in januari compar with a deficit of 112 mln dlr in februari last year , provision bank of korea figur show . the current account in the two month of januari and februari swung to a surplu of 1.1 billion dlr from a deficit of 494 mln dlr in the same 1986 period . the februari trade surplu narrow to 235 mln dlr from 582 mln in januari compar with a deficit of 98 mln dlr a year ago . the overal balanc of payment surplu rose to 840 mln dlr in februari from 716 mln in januari and 76 mln in februari 1986. export were 2.86 billion dlr in februari against 2.83 billion in januari and 2.23 billion in februari last year . import were 2.63 billion against 2.25 billion and 2.32 billion . the februari invis trade surplu rose to 109 mln dlr from 24 mln in januari and compar with a deficit of 74 mln a year ago . the transfer payment surplu widen to 75 mln dlr in februari from 73 mln in januari and 60 mln a year ago . the long-term capit account surplu wa 198 mln dlr in februari against 211 mln in januari and 55 mln in februari last year . the short-term capit account surplu wa 87 mln dlr against 46 mln and 158 mln . the error and omiss account left a surplu of 840 mln dlr in februari against deficit of 220 mln in januari and 25 mln in februari 1986 .